<p><b>What are the different types of biomedical instruments?</b> TYPES OF BIOMEDICAL INSTRUMENTS: Diagnostic equipment includes medical imaging machines, used to aid in diagnosis. . Examples are ultrasound and MRI machines, PET and CT scanners, and x-ray machines. Therapeutic equipment includes infusion pumps, medical lasers and LASIK surgical machines.</p>
